{"_id":"041f2032-228c-4830-9a02-f9f89b53184d","type":"ability","name":"Explorer","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/expedition.svg","system":{"skill":"Expedition","name":"Explorer","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"You gain a boon to all checks related to navigating and surviving in an uncharted area (or at least one for which you do not have maps and with which you are not familiar).","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"","skill_id":"expedition"}}
{"_id":"11843ed5-b2f6-4973-9332-0035f92f72a7","type":"ability","name":"Diligent Planning","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/expedition.svg","system":{"skill":"Expedition","name":"Diligent Planning","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"If you spend an hour preparing for a long journey you will make that day, you and all your allies gain a Boon on checks made to resist harsh weather, difficult conditions, or exertion.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"expedition"}}
{"_id":"1e01f3b2-a01f-4f09-8d1c-f8ed61d85da5","type":"ability","name":"Well Prepared","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/expedition.svg","system":{"skill":"Expedition","name":"Well Prepared","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"You are always well prepared for each day. Once per Venture you may use this ability to retroactively have planned for a particular outcome. For example if caught in a snowstorm you may have brought warm clothes for everyone, or if you need an antitoxin you have one in your pack. The GM will decide what is reasonable for this ability, but it should be something you would have had access to, and not particularly expensive.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"expedition"}}
{"_id":"3615c89a-3a13-439f-a51b-d57479fab994","type":"ability","name":"Find Another Way","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/expedition.svg","system":{"skill":"Expedition","name":"Find Another Way","rank":"3","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"When faced with a navigational hazard such as a path blocked with boulders, a broken bridge, or a difficult to scale cliff, you may make a check to find another way around. If the GM allows it, you take a Consequence as you spend additional time finding the way around.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"expedition"}}
{"_id":"36b13cc8-32e0-4de9-befc-46f78b13b6a2","type":"ability","name":"Logistical Genius","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/expedition.svg","system":{"skill":"Expedition","name":"Logistical Genius","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"You may help an ally even when you yourself are busy. When you help an ally, gain a Boon to the skill.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"","skill_id":"expedition"}}
{"_id":"4c988155-1453-4e05-b9bd-242841c6b9b9","type":"skill","name":"Expedition","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/expedition.svg","system":{"skill_id":"expedition","domain":"Expertise","rank":1,"stat":"intuition","description":"The expedition skill is used in planning and executing expeditions and travel, as well as navigation and exploration. It can be used to handle the logistics of anything from a solo trek through the jungle to the movements of an entire army."}}
{"_id":"9c7d3ce6-a3d6-4b13-a781-dc6d38aac848","type":"ability","name":"Field Quartermaster","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/expedition.svg","system":{"skill":"Expedition","name":"Field Quartermaster","rank":"3","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"You can make do with limited resources, including those found in nature. If you spend an hour searching for materials and crafting, you can create basic materials such as simple tools, basic light armour or weapons, rope, warm clothes, or other similar items. You may also use this to repair more complex objects even if you lack the proper tools or supplies. Items created or repaired with this ability last only until the end of the Venture.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"","skill_id":"expedition"}}
{"_id":"be1d4652-b3bd-4019-ab70-f8864cadc2bf","type":"ability","name":"Luxury Camp","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/expedition.svg","system":{"skill":"Expedition","name":"Luxury Camp","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"When you and your allies rest in a shelter you have created or found, all healing checks have a Boon. If you sleep in it, you all recover an additional point of Endurance.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"","skill_id":"expedition"}}
{"_id":"c1140599-0ea1-4601-bc12-6cce8f84e5f5","type":"ability","name":"Pull Together","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/expedition.svg","system":{"skill":"Expedition","name":"Pull Together","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"When you and your allies are attempting to traverse difficult terrain, survive harsh conditions and weather, or navigate a hazard such as passing through toxic sewers or scaling a cliff and must make a group check (everybody rolls), you may roll your skill die an additional time and add it to the result of the lowest check other than your own. You may do this after seeing the results.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"expedition"}}
{"_id":"d6527e8a-6bd3-4a76-bf90-48d8085250a8","type":"ability","name":"Safe Haven","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/expedition.svg","system":{"skill":"Expedition","name":"Safe Haven","rank":"3","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"You can find ideal shelter in the wilderness. When your party sleeps in a shelter you have created or found, foes have a Bane on any check to find you. If the Consequence Tracker is positive, you can spend 2 Vim to remove a Consequence as your shelter provides a restful sleep.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"","skill_id":"expedition"}}
